text: Vítězslav Lahr (born 15 July 1929) was a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
